metadata.name: Cool Fools #1
metadata.description: Cool Fools is a 4444 NFT Collection created by a group of real-world friends who decided to collaborate to bring the Fools to life. Each Cool Fool will be a unique NFT on the Ethereum blockchain, consisting of a unique combination of hand-drawn characteristics that distinguish them. Not only would owning a Cool Fool make you more dumb, but it will also allow you to vote on community-driven features, goods, and online events.
